{"tid":1832082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳民眾： 不怕，現在黨的關懷，絕對相信我們中國政府！","createTime":"2020-01-21T02:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T09:49:52.000Z","uid":240448,"like":173,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac00bd19297d01623ce41cde9861d0dc212c6ae","tid":1832082,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcKhgkq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcKhgkq.png&h=37295dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接收了武漢肺炎患者的深圳市第三人民醫院，不少人都無戴口罩，包括醫護人員，就連隔離病房那一層都能自出自入，只是有一道屏風隔開隔離區域，不少玻璃窗打開了通風。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xz2e2ZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXz2e2ZY.png&h=a458902e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmWrT6H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmWrT6H.png&h=6ebe9fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPepFMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPepFMM.png&h=e8c6b20a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hpdy6Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hpdy6Q.png&h=c091c5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPYRkMT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPYRkMT.png&h=87a3c3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了深圳的一宗病例，北京亦在周一凌晨通報兩宗確診個案，不過我們在北京去過三間醫院，即使是人流密集的三甲醫院，防護都未見加強。廣州的醫院同樣無加強防疫。不少民眾都說未驚過。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「絕對相信我們中國政府。」<br />\n「不怕，現在黨的關懷，到處都預防了。現在黨的領導下關心我們，老百姓最好，一年比一年好。」</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ud9MT7i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fud9MT7i.png&h=29f2b9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFhZuFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFhZuFJ.png&h=f3d1d5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNNZuFO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNNZuFO.png&h=929d18dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXmLqec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXmLqec.png&h=ca3c9170&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRRb5eg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRRb5eg.png&h=b6beba27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uCR5em.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uCR5em.png&h=6803454b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NHq9F8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NHq9F8.png&h=26b8dc8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續。當地衛健委周一凌晨通布，過去的周末當地新增確診136宗病例，其中一人死亡，累計死亡人數增加至3人。截至周一晚，全國病例急增至201宗。<br />\n另外，深圳和浙江衛健委亦分別發現8宗和5宗出現呼吸道感染症狀的懷疑個案。<br />\n<br />\n浙江省和北上廣深四個市已啟動防控措施，包括在出入境口岸啟動體溫監測。另外有武漢飛澳門的班機亦被指所有乘客到埗後，要在機上量完體溫才可以下機。"},{"pid":"c6b063836bc86639dd085d1253f9f3e9629dfe86","tid":1832082,"uid":240448,"like":196,"dislike":5,"score":191,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0YJWms.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0YJWms.png&h=05187b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇士可唔可以帶番個口罩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5d65291e09898a47f531b4a2eb7dc2a3c7e6ca","tid":1832082,"uid":74361,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:16:58.000Z","msg":"支持，我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" c