一凌晨通布，過去的周末當地新增確診136宗病例，其中一人死亡，累計死亡人數增加至3人。截至周一晚，全國病例急增至201宗。<br />\n另外，深圳和浙江衛健委亦分別發現8宗和5宗出現呼吸道感染症狀的懷疑個案。<br />\n<br />\n浙江省和北上廣深四個市已啟動防控措施，包括在出入境口岸啟動體溫監測。另外有武漢飛澳門的班機亦被指所有乘客到埗後，要在機上量完體溫才可以下機。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"話黨唔好仲唔被自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb7905b8abb140ef1641afb69c2911e7c522c55","tid":1832082,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3736becc710223590fe30a2caf55535a47516a8d","tid":1832082,"uid":49699,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5d8a0a22de6ae8e8f52e81fdcf2833ae17c24cbf","tid":1832082,"uid":240448,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E639RZf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE639RZf.png&h=362cb264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pScbkSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpScbkSB.png&h=28188299&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tx8mH5X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTx8mH5X.png&h=101ee6d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"所以支那人死哂都唔值得可憐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"你都可憐唔到, 因為&quot;無人死&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441af023de55703c47924a7bf5a8efcfd04a8ffe","tid":1832082,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"點解可以洗腦洗得咁緊要..."},{"pid":"4979136e39a7eca5f31e7eba2c0655f6ac80b0cc","tid":1832082,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"支爆近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982f01a864d6c866ef97e1f10384b62f7518b63b","tid":1832082,"uid":342786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:14:44.000Z","msg":"曲直難